  'Very little GPS data was recorded. Finish this run anyway?': { ro: 'Au fost înregistrate foarte puține date GPS. Închei totuși alergarea?', th: 'บันทึกข้อมูล GPS ได้น้อยมาก ต้องการจบการวิ่งอยู่หรือไม่?' },
  'Cancel this run and permanently discard its recorded track?': { ro: 'Anulezi alergarea și ștergi definitiv traseul înregistrat?', th: 'ยกเลิกการวิ่งและลบเส้นทางที่บันทึกไว้อย่างถาวรหรือไม่?' },
  'Finish at the current distance? Orbit will analyse the useful work completed.': { ro: 'Închei la distanța actuală? Orbit va analiza munca utilă realizată.', th: 'จบที่ระยะปัจจุบันหรือไม่ Orbit จะวิเคราะห์งานที่มีประโยชน์ซึ่งทำเสร็จแล้ว' },
  'Waiting for a precise GPS sample.': { ro: 'Se așteaptă un semnal GPS precis.', th: 'กำลังรอสัญญาณ GPS ที่แม่นยำ' },
  'Weak GPS. Move into a clearer area if possible.': { ro: 'Semnal GPS slab. Mergi într-o zonă mai deschisă dacă poți.', th: 'สัญญาณ GPS อ่อน หากทำได้ให้ไปยังพื้นที่โล่งกว่า' },
  'You have completed the useful planned stimulus. There is no need to extend today’s session.': { ro: 'Ai realizat stimulul util planificat. Nu este nevoie să prelungești sesiunea de azi.', th: 'คุณทำงานตามแผนที่มีประโยชน์ครบแล้ว ไม่จำเป็นต้องยืดการฝึกวันนี้' },
  'Begin deliberately easy. Today’s value comes from restraint.': { ro: 'Începe intenționat ușor. Valoarea de azi vine din control.', th: 'ตั้งใจเริ่มเบา คุณค่าของวันนี้มาจากการยับยั้งตัวเอง' },
  'Settle in gradually. There is no need to win the first kilometre.': { ro: 'Intră treptat în ritm. Nu trebuie să câștigi primul kilometru.', th: 'ค่อย ๆ เข้าจังหวะ ไม่จำเป็นต้องชนะกิโลเมตรแรก' },
  'Keep the effort conversational. Protect the next demanding session.': { ro: 'Păstrează efortul conversațional. Protejează următoarea sesiune solicitantă.', th: 'รักษาระดับที่ยังพูดคุยได้ เพื่อปกป้องการฝึกหนักครั้งถัดไป' },
  'Settle into the intended range rather than accelerating immediately.': { ro: 'Așază-te în intervalul dorit fără să accelerezi imediat.', th: 'เข้าสู่ช่วงเป้าหมายก่อน แทนการเร่งทันที' },
  'Keep the work repetitions controlled and make recovery sections genuinely easy.': { ro: 'Păstrează repetările controlate și fă secțiunile de recuperare cu adevărat ușoare.', th: 'ควบคุมช่วงทำงาน และทำช่วงพักให้เบาจริง ๆ' },
  'Let pace change with the gradient while effort remains controlled.': { ro: 'Lasă ritmul să se schimbe cu panta, păstrând efortul controlat.', th: 'ปล่อยให้เพซเปลี่ยนตามความชัน โดยยังควบคุมระดับแรง' },
  'GPS is still stabilising. Run by effort until pace becomes reliable.': { ro: 'GPS-ul încă se stabilizează. Aleargă după efort până când ritmul devine fiabil.', th: 'GPS กำลังปรับความแม่นยำ ให้วิ่งตามระดับแรงจนกว่าเพซจะเชื่อถือได้' },
  'Stay with the mission. Faster is only useful when the session calls for it.': { ro: 'Rămâi la scopul sesiunii. Viteza mai mare este utilă doar când sesiunea o cere.', th: 'ยึดเป้าหมายของการฝึก ความเร็วมากขึ้นมีประโยชน์เมื่อแผนต้องการเท่านั้น' },
  'A return path becomes available after enough movement is recorded.': { ro: 'Traseul de întoarcere devine disponibil după ce se înregistrează suficientă mișcare.', th: 'เส้นทางกลับจะพร้อมหลังจากบันทึกการเคลื่อนไหวได้เพียงพอ' },
  'Return-to-start guidance now follows your recorded path in reverse.': { ro: 'Ghidarea spre start urmează acum traseul înregistrat în sens invers.', th: 'การนำทางกลับจุดเริ่มจะย้อนตามเส้นทางที่บันทึกไว้' },
  'Approaching the planned finish.': { ro: 'Te apropii de finalul planificat.', th: 'กำลังเข้าใกล้จุดสิ้นสุดตามแผน' },
  'Location permission was denied. You can still plan manually or import GPX.': { ro: 'Permisiunea de localizare a fost refuzată. Poți planifica manual sau importa GPX.', th: 'ไม่อนุญาตตำแหน่ง คุณยังวางเส้นทางเองหรือนำเข้า GPX ได้' },
  'Location is currently unavailable.': { ro: 'Locația nu este disponibilă momentan.', th: 'ขณะนี้ไม่สามารถใช้ตำแหน่งได้' },
  'Location timed out. Move to an open area and try again.': { ro: 'Localizarea a expirat. Mergi într-o zonă deschisă și încearcă din nou.', th: 'การค้นหาตำแหน่งหมดเวลา ไปยังพื้นที่โล่งแล้วลองอีกครั้ง' },
  'Location is not supported by this browser.': { ro: 'Localizarea nu este acceptată de acest browser.', th: 'เบราว์เซอร์นี้ไม่รองรับตำแหน่ง' },
